QUI for MPlayer
Ben Nemec (cybertron@nemebean.com)
Distributed under the GPLv3.  See LICENSE for details.
http://sourceforge.net/apps/trac/qui4mplayer/wiki

Installation:
Simply enter "./setup.py install" (without the quotes) as root in this directory.

Uninstallation:
This is more complicated.  Full instructions are available at http://sourceforge.net/apps/trac/qui4mplayer/wiki/InstallAndUninstall
Note that in most cases it isn't necessary to uninstall QUI as it should not interfere with anything else